# Database Requirement Analysis

## Tables Required

1. Student
   - student_id
   - name
   - email
   - password

2. Subject
   - subject_id
   - subject_name
   - faculty_name

3. Assignment
   - assignment_id
   - title
   - description
   - due_date
   - status

4. StudyPlan
   - plan_id
   - study_date
   - start_time
   - end_time

5. Progress
   - progress_id
   - task_name
   - completion_status

6. User
   - user_id
   - username
   - password
   - role
